{"tid":2340102,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iOS/ iPadOS「標示工具遮資料正確用法","createTime":"2020-12-25T07:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T08:33:37.000Z","uid":197393,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a4107d59a15889ba1c14ba023b8b2e5d8f2134","tid":2340102,"uid":197393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T07:24:34.000Z","msg":"成日都有啲用咗iOS/ iPadOS嘅「標示Markup」工具去遮資料但俾人較下曝光 亮度之類嘅設定show 返啲字出嚟<br />\n例如：<br />\nApple Pay 八達通死左ser?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aHfKhtV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aHfKhtV</a><br />\n#23 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n「標示Markup」工具有三種筆，分別係鋼筆<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06ktqAz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06ktqAz.png&h=dea0574d&s={SIZE}\" /> 、螢光筆<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZf5sO1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZf5sO1.png&h=c1440cd6&s={SIZE}\" />、鉛筆<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yw1cSfH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyw1cSfH.png&h=6a051c70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信有唔少人會貪方便用粗啲嘅黑色螢光筆去遮資料，不過用過highlighter嘅都知highlighter係透明㗎啦<br />\n有啲人會話有iOS/ iPadOS「個marker係透明」，其實只係你揀錯咗螢光筆<br />\n<br />\n鋼筆係實色，所以想遮資料係應該用鋼色，唔係螢光筆<br />\n而鋼筆嘅粗幼都有得較<br />\n<br />\n用咗鋼筆就算一下就遮到字，點較都唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rJjBzv4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrJjBzv4.png&h=8be4ea6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3083e98923ecb149dd61f2667eb2fbcc4391389","tid":2340102,"uid":197393,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T07:25:15.000Z","msg":"屌你幅圖掉轉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac710d492cba01bbada39d302bd5e08a2a6d9879","tid":2340102,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T07:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"106d1af4350bf59f5fd5f61ee2c77a16fe6d89f3","tid":2340102,"uid":197393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac710d492cba01bbada39d302bd5e08a2a6d9879","tid":2340102,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T07:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"今次真係用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca56bae6ec629d2b28016747ce3084b5fef0597","tid":2340102,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"長知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08137f7d400488e80797ca3921810f9babc58b0","tid":2340102,"uid":11918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"麻煩置頂，重點係㩒多下枝筆就可以較粗幼度。"},{"pid":"3f3b60c87c6621195fa428a66f83fc814bad7bf2","tid":2340102,"uid":341649,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:33:37.000Z","msg":"到底有幾多智障唔知道highlighter 係透明㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"f08137f7d400488e80797ca3921810f9babc58b0","tid":2340102,"uid":11918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"麻煩置頂，重點係㩒多下枝筆就可以較粗幼度。"}}